rows.label: tev065601_JNK0010
rows.name: Inquire[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL0011
rows.name: Ask Go Belg about the Wrothians.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_JNK0020
rows.name: Discuss[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL0021
rows.name: Ask Go Belg if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0001
rows.name:
I serve the Ganglion no longer, and as such have no
quarrel with you.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0002
rows.name:
But still, it is not my place to judge you friend or foe.
Until Prince Jiarg wills it, I cannot tell you about our
people.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0005
rows.name:
A human? Pah. I did not want your kind to see such a
pitiful display.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0006
rows.name:
When it comes to the sword, we can hold our own
against any. But as for medicine, we command not
even a fraction of the Ganglion's technology.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0007
rows.name:
Now that we stand alone, we lack the faculties to
cure even the simple illness of a child.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0008
rows.name:
What are we to do? Must we surrender again to those
fiends just to save our own?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL1011
rows.name:
Ask Go Belg for his thoughts on
friendship treaties with xenoforms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL1021
rows.name: Ask Go Belg if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0009
rows.name: Prince Jiarg has decided to fight alongside humans![ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0010
rows.name:
They fought valiantly during the clash in Sylvalum,
exhibiting strength not only of body, but of character.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0011
rows.name: I support our prince's decision wholeheartedly.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0014
rows.name: Hmm...[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0015
rows.name:
That is strange. I swear that I have seen your face
somewhere before.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0016
rows.name: Have we met in battle? No... It was something else.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0017
rows.name: Mmm... This is going to bother me.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL2011
rows.name:
Ask Go Belg for his thoughts on
friendship treaties with xenoforms.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_SEL2021
rows.name: Ask Go Belg if anything is troubling him.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0018
rows.name:
My respect for the old laws dissuades me from
embracing new things. Call it a character flaw.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0019
rows.name:
Perhaps if I had been more open-minded, I might have
found a way to resist the Ganglion instead of obeying
like a meekling.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0020
rows.name:
But the young of Wroth give me hope. Your city may
provide them new experience and new ways to make
our people stronger.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0021
rows.name:
As long as they remember to honor our important
traditions and duties as well.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0025
rows.name:
Gi Ziordo and Gi Ziorde are still out there somewhere,
pursuing their quest of self-betterment.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0026
rows.name:
But I know them. They may clash along the journey,
but they will never part ways again.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0027
rows.name: ...Hmm? What will I do?[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0028
rows.name:
Well, many of my people have moved to New LA.
I suppose I will stay here and protect Prince Jiarg
while I wait for my pupils to return.[ST:wait ]

rows.label: tev065601_MSG0029
rows.name:
This is the final task for an old soldier, you see.
If any dare attack us, I will fight them until this body
ceases to obey my orders! Ha ha ha![ST:wait ]
